# Summary
This documentation explains how to create, edit, and manage Amplitude dashboards, including adding charts, cohorts, Session Replays, images, and videos, as well as designating dashboards as "official" sources of truth, commenting on dashboards, and performing administrative functions like refreshing, downloading, and archiving.

